    a) fr das Usenet (Newsgroups):

@alabel nntpserv
       @{0U}NNTP-Server (Usenet-Server)@{0}
       - Name (frei w„hlbar, z.B. 'News Club Internet').
       - Serveradresse (z.B. 'news.club-internet.fr').
